Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我已經...無法飛翔了
